            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1223899</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>AI 发展日益先进，现在已经可以做到「换头」技术。今日小编想和大家分享「Change Face With AI」这个小工具，用家可以用这个工具来帮相片换脸。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225044" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225072" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/20240318192457-694x459.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/20240318192457-694x459.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/20240318192457.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这个 AI 会自动帮用家「就角度」，原图中的人脸不一定要与目标图片角度一样</p><p>连结：<a href="https://www.changeface.online/">https://www.changeface.online/</a></p><p>这个工具非常易用，进入 Change Face With AI 网站后会看见下图的画面。上方 faceSource （绿色框示）是要换脸的图片，意思是这张图片里面的人脸会被贴到另一张照片上；faceDestination （红色框示）的人脸就会被 faceSource 的人脸取缔。如果你图片中只有一个人的话，就不用理会 faceSource 下方的 sourceFaceId，如果你的图片有多于一个人，就需要输入你想换脸的对象，由图片最左边开始计为 1，例如图片有 3 个人，而你想用中间的脸的话就输入 2。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225015" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1-1-3-594x580.jpg" alt="" width="594" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1-1-3-594x580.jpg 594w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1-1-3.jpg 922w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 594px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> </p><p>小编就尝试用 Weak 妹的脸替换特朗普的脸，看看这个 AI 效果如何。上传相片后点击「Submit」，静候约 5 分钟就能够看到结果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225030" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/20240318164429-587x580.jpg" alt="" width="587" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/20240318164429-587x580.jpg 587w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/20240318164429.jpg 911w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 587px" /></p><p>小编觉得这个 AI 手工较「粗糙」，有不少瑕疵，不过以玩乐性质来说已足以搏君一笑。最令小编惊讶的是 Change Face With AI 可以改变 faceSource 的表情，本来 weak 妹没有露齿笑，变脸后就跟特朗普一样露齿笑。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225018" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/unwire-1710753224-458x580.jpg" alt="" width="458" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/unwire-1710753224-458x580.jpg 458w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/unwire-1710753224.jpg 711w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 458px" /></p><p>小编另外再尝试用一张有多个面孔的图片来换脸，看看 AI 是否真的能够判断小编想用哪一张脸。今次我要将水哥的脸换到 Elon Musk 上。由左边数起，水哥排第 3，于是我就在 sourceFaceId 上输入「3」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225034" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1710755537-328x580.jpeg" alt="" width="328" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1710755537-328x580.jpeg 328w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1710755537.jpeg 509w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 328px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225036" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2-1-588x580.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2-1-588x580.jpg 588w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2-1.jpg 913w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 588px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小编输入了「3」（红色箭嘴示），想将水哥的脸换到 Elon Musk 上</p><p>实测后发现这个 AI 真的可以辨识到用家想要换哪一张脸，成功生成「Elon 水」的图片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225042" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1-1-4-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1-1-4-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1-1-4.jpg 901w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1-1-4-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2>总结：简单易用，略嫌等候时间较长</h2><p>这款换脸 AI 非常容易用，只需要上传图片，静候 3-5 分钟就可以「换头」，不过效果就仅限用于开玩笑的地步，还未到以假乱真的程度，而且其等待时间「不老实」，经常会延误，例如本来它告诉小编表示 253 秒后就能生成图片，但最终超过其预定时间（见下图）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225060" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/20240318181617-554x580.jpg" alt="" width="554" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/20240318181617-554x580.jpg 554w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/20240318181617.jpg 611w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 554px" /></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/07/m3-macbook-air-%e8%a9%95%e6%b8%ac/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">M3 Macbook Air 评测　AI 生成图像、影片实试</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/google-imagefx/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】「ImageFX」Google AI 绘图工具教学，免费使用、一键生成旅行／食物图片</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/19/openai-gpt-store-2/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】GPT Store 正式开放 ChatGPT AI 女朋友 + 一张相帮你谂食谱</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/18/change-face-with-ai/fun-tech/">【教学】Change Face With AI 换脸术，一键即换头</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
